Do you know what is really going into your trolley? Learn how to decode food
labels and spot the techniques used to trick you into buying unhealthy food.
This two-hour workshop will help you make healthy choices while shopping. This
* Reading food labels and nutritional information on food products
* Learn about the Glycaemic Index of foods and how it impacts your blood glucose levels
* Portion sizes and the amount of carbohydrate in foods
